How to use HolsterAid
- Open "Sound and Alert Profiles"
- Select "Change Sounds and Alerts"
- Select "Profile Management"
- Select "Normal"
- Select "Phone"
- Select desired in-holster Notifier tone, Volume, etc.
- Select "Play sound: In holster"
- Escape and Save
- Select "Other Applications - Notifiers"
- Select "HolsterAid"
- Select desired out-of-holster Notifier tone, Volume, etc.
- Escape and Save

- Open HolsterAid
- Select "Test" and see if out-of-holster settings are what you want
